qtxdg-tools-4.3.0 / 2025-11-05
===============================
 * Bumped the version and dependencies.

qtxdg-tools-4.2.0 / 2025-04-17
===============================
 * Modernized the strings by using `QLatin1StringView` and string operators. Also, removed the `xdgmacros` header.

qtxdg-tools-4.1.0 / 2024-11-05
===============================
 * Do not include `file://` when opening local files.

qtxdg-tools-4.0.0 / 2024-04-17
===============================
 * Ported to Qt6.

